body_html: When modifying examples, you might need to tailor the build to make sure all the kernel libraries (which use a registration pattern) are being included. With that said, this question is better asked on StackOverflow since it is not a bug or feature request. There is a larger community that reads questions there. You can also likely search for many similar issues.

body: When modifying examples, you might need to tailor the build to make sure all the kernel libraries (which use a registration pattern) are being included. With that said, this question is better asked on  [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow) since it is not a  bug or feature request. There is a larger community that reads questions there. You can also likely search for many similar issues.
